features: 【Comes In 2 Boxes】 In order to make sure that this 7 piece dining table set will arrive at your home in good condition, we split the dining table and chairs set into 2 packages. Box A - Table, Box B - 6 Chairs. And it may arrive at your place at different time.❗❗❗ Please be patient and contact us promptly if there are any problems.

【Specifications & Easy Assembly】Table size: 51.2”L x 27.6”W x 29.5”H, Chairs size: 38.6”H x 15.7”W x 16.7”L. This chair and table set has intuitive illustrations and instructions. each screw and pin has its own code, it is easy to understand the assembly progress. it will not cost you a lot of time and can save your energy.

【Tempered Glass Tabletop】 The tabletop of this dining table and chairs for 6 is made of tempered glass, which is easy to clean if there are water stains, coffee, oil stains and other residues are poured on the table. And it always looks like brand new after cleaning.

【Family Friendly Dining Sets】This dinning table sets for 6 includes 1 table and 6 chairs for the whole family(for 6 or less) to enjoy. The seat of the chair features a contoured stream that perfectly fits your buttocks and supports your body. The mid-backrest syncs up with the natural curvature of the spine, such an ergonomic design allows you to sit cozily every time.

【Durable & Well Made】 There are no complicated design, but it's perfect, the glass tabletop is embedded in the iron structural frame, making the entire kitchen dining table set stylish and functional. And chairs are filled with sponge to ensure its comfort. it's light and dose not take up space, and it can be placed in any large and small space. Chairs can be tucked under the table to save space.

【Various Usage】This kitchen table and chairs for 6 is ideal for everyday dining and gatherings of family and friends. There are 3 colors available for your choice, black/marble/white. You can choose the desired set to match with your home decor style. And this dining room table set for 6 can be used in home, kitchen, living room and dining room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars An ok table set for the price.
reviews.reviewText: The table and chairs are relatively well made, chairs could be a little bit longer in the seat and a little better padded, but fine for dinners and things like that. The table could be a bit wider and longer, but the height is ok, and it all fits together pretty well. Unfortunately the finishes was all scratched up and scuffed, which, since it's jet black, is an issue, the box was fine, but the metal still had enough room to scrape around apparently. If you need a six person table and chair set that you aren't going to stare very hard at, then this will work on a budget.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very sturdy and heavy duty will last a lifetime easy to set up well packaged for shipping I sent it to Jamaica just set it up this pass week very beautiful and make a statement just the right size for 6 people not too huge chairs are light but strong can easily move with one hand. I recommend this dinner set price is very affordable the glass on the top weights a ton I love it I'm now going to get another one for myself

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Not great long term
reviews.reviewText: We have had this table for six months. We purchased two of them in order to create a long sleek table style. However, after o Lu six months of use, the table has become “see through” where scratches were sustained. The chairs are also falling apart. I must constantly redo the bolts or it’ll literally fall apart. Even when done 100% correct, the chairs wiggle and wobble. They are difficult to clean.In the future we will invest in a wooden table and chair set. Going for the inexpensive version is now costing us in the long term.
